original_title: Richmond: Bloomingdale Road - Clay Pit Road
text:
(1) Bloomingdale Road, west side, between Clay Pit and Sharrotts Road, showing (right) the Rossville African Methodist Episcopal Church and a house adjoining to the south which bears No. 570.

September 23, 1927.

P. L. Sperr.

(2) The same, another view.

September 23, 1927.

P. L. Sperr.
